    <abstract>
      <t>        Ping is a widely deployed Operation, Administration, and Maintenance
        (OAM) mechanism in networks.  This document describes a mechanism
        for detecting data-plane failures using Ping in RFC7348 VXLAN based
        EVPN networks.

	 </t>
